sections.text:
86-1046.911 service, defined.

911 service means the service a public safety answering point uses to receive and process 911 calls over a 911 service system.

SourceLaws 2016, LB938, § 18;R.S.1943, (2024), § 86-1018;Laws 2025, LB362, § 28.Effective Date: September 3, 2025
